doctype html
html(lang="en-gb")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    meta(http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible", content="ie=edge")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="style.css", data-inline)
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat")
  body
    table(class="header" style="width: 100%")
      tbody
        tr
          td(style="padding-left: 16px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 16px;")
            img(
              src='https://res.cloudinary.com/dg1royeho/image/upload/c_limit,h_144/logo_no_lines_WHITE_png_sbh3l7.png'
              width="63"
              height="72"
              style="height: 72px; width: 63px;"
            )
          td(style="padding-right: 16px;")
            h1 Ticket Confirmation
    p Dear #{name},
    if order
      p Thank you for your purchase! This e-mail confirms the successful purchase of the <b>#{ticket.type.name}</b> ticket for order #{order.code}.
    else
      p This e-mail is a confirmation of your <b>#{ticket.type.name}</b> ticket.
    p We can't wait to see you during this exciting event!
    br
    h2 Save the Date
    p
      | Don't forget that this year's conference officially starts on <b>#{edition.startDate}</b>.
      | Time of the morning registration will be announced in the agenda.
    p We will be situated in <b>#{venue.name}</b>, which is located at
    pre
      b #{venue.location}
    br
    h2 On the Day
    p During the morning registration, you will have to present your ticket in order to check-in.
    p The cool-and-hip way of doing this is by downloading the <b>Poland 2.0 Summit app</b>, available on Android and iOS.
    table(class="center")
      tbody
        tr
          td
            a(href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.poland20.app")
              img(
                src="https://play.google.com/intl/en_gb/badges/images/generic/en_badge_web_generic.png"
                width="155"
                height="60"
                style="height: 60px; width: 155px;"
              )
          td
            a(href="https://apps.apple.com/gb/app/poland-2-0-summit/id1443577236")
              img(
                src="https://developer.apple.com/app-store/marketing/guidelines/images/badge-example-preferred_2x.png",
                width="124"
                height="42"
                style="height: 42px; width: 124px;"
              )
    p Once you're in the app, enter your ticket code:
    table(class="center")
      tbody
        tr
          td
            h3 #{ticket.code}
    p
      u Keep it safe in case something goes wrong!
    p We highly recommend you check-in using our app, as you will gain access to our <b>priority queue</b>!
    p Alternatively, you can present this QR code at the registration desk in the normal queue:
    table(class="center")
      tbody
        tr
          td
            img(
              src=`https://chart.googleapis.com/chart?cht=qr&chl=${ticket.code}&chs=280x280&choe=UTF-8&chld=L|2`
              style="height: 280px; width: 280px;"
            )
    br
    h2 Other Stuff
    p If you have any questions or concerns, feel free to contact us by replying to this e-mail (<a href="mailto:contact@poland20.com">contact@poland20.com</a>).
    p Otherwise, prepare yourself for a fantastic weekend to come!
    p Follow us on social media to stay up-to-date with news regarding the conference.
    p Visit our website (<a href="https://poland20.com">poland20.com</a>) to discover the agenda, speakers, and to learn more about Poland 2.0 Summit.
    table(class="footer center")
      tbody
        tr
          td
            a(href="https://www.facebook.com/Poland20Summit/")
              img(
                src="https://iconmonstr.com/wp-content/g/gd/makefg.php?i=../assets/preview/2012/png/iconmonstr-facebook-4.png&r=198&g=61&b=87"
                width="48"
                height="48"
                style="height: 48px; width: 48px;"
              )
          td
            a(href="https://www.instagram.com/poland20summit/")
              img(
                src="https://iconmonstr.com/wp-content/g/gd/makefg.php?i=../assets/preview/2016/png/iconmonstr-instagram-11.png&r=198&g=61&b=87"
                width="48"
                height="48"
                style="height: 48px; width: 48px;"
              )
          td
            a(href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/poland20/")
              img(
                src="https://iconmonstr.com/wp-content/g/gd/makefg.php?i=../assets/preview/2012/png/iconmonstr-linkedin-3.png&r=198&g=61&b=87"
                width="48"
                height="48"
                style="height: 48px; width: 48px;"
              )


